sections.description:
This plugin can be called and displays Gravity Forms Entries Using a simple URL: https://www.mydomain.com/wp-json/gfdata/v1/date/MM-DD-YYYY

This plugin can be called and displays WP Security Audit Log Entries Using a simple URL: https://www.mydomain.com/wp-json/alog/v1/date/MM-DD-YYYY

This plugin can be called and displays JSON Sitemap using a simple URL: https://www.mydomain.com/wp-json/sitemap/v1/generate

Replace MM-DD-YYYY with any date and only entries on or after that date will be displayed.

NOTE: Do not use this plugin to display sensitive information.
sections.installation:
This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.
1# – Install plugin via wp-admin backend or via FTP and activate. Thats all.
